{"word":"G952 - βέβηλος - bébēlos - beb'-ay-los - Profane","slug":"G952","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βέβηλος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bébēlos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>beb'-ay-los"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Profane"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B2;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03B2;&#x03B7;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - bebe&#x0304;los</b> - <i>beb'-ay-los</i><p/>From the base of <a href=\"#/G939\">G939</a> and <b>&#x03B2;&#x03B7;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C2;</b> <b>be&#x0304;los</b> (a <i>threshold</i>); <i>accessible</i> (as by <i>crossing the door way</i>), that is, (by implication of Jewish notions) <i>heathenish</i>, <i>wicked:</i> - profane (person)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G953\">G953</a>"}]}